title: Is the sun setting on the Australian dream?
text: Is the sun setting on the Australian dream? Expats are choosing to move from Oz to the UK, Europe and New Zealand. But why? Could warm evenings and sharing a beer in the great outdoors no longer be enough for British expats? Photo: Adam Pretty/Getty Images By Hannah Ewens
